#include <iostream>
#include <sstream>
using namespace std;

int main(){
	ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);
	int n,q,temp;
	stringstream ss;
	cin>>n>>q;
	int maxi=-1,mini=1e9+10;
	for(int i=0;i<n;i++){
		cin>>temp;
		if (temp<mini) mini = temp;
		if (temp>maxi) maxi = temp;
	}
	for(int i=0;i<q;i++){
		int t;
		cin>>t;
		if (mini<=t && t<=maxi) ss<<"Yes\n";
		else ss<<"No\n";
	}
	cout<<ss.str()<<endl;
}
